fields.message:
All ACF global elements should be created in the 'Customizations' tab. These can include:
- google map embed code
- global address
- global email address
- global phone

For call tracking purposes, the global phone number can be utilized as a shortcode by pasting the following function into the functions.php file:

function addGlobalNumber() {
        return get_field('phone_number','options');
    }
add_shortcode('globalnumber', 'addGlobalNumber');

This is referenced by using the following shortcode: [globalnumber]
